{"id": "1453292220974239857", "channel_id": "1453292220974239857", "type": 0, "author_id": "1139202390919233566", "author_name": "akkom730", "author_bot": false, "content": "上次問過六分儀\n有人留言說有星星標誌的造物不會被收藏\n今天活動開的關卡(最後一關)，給的所有造物都有星星標誌(祂的神諭+除外)\n也都可以在收藏找到\n\n所以，到底怎樣的造物會被收藏？\n以玩家的歌詞觀點是希望全部收藏的，包括活動、主線限定的造物", "timestamp": "2025-12-24T07:44:26.344000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1453292221888462859", "filename": "IMG_4621.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 812038, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1453292220974239857/1453292221888462859/IMG_4621.png?ex=69ff8e9a&is=69fe3d1a&hm=6a7e1e183ceda038ccb5126f27248ab1da95cbfeab5f0e0b38e908a216c1fd63&"}, {"id": "1453292222249435166", "filename": "IMG_4628.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 839623, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1453292220974239857/1453292222249435166/IMG_4628.png?ex=69ff8e9a&is=69fe3d1a&hm=50295262239cd0775679a5c8eecc36ee27ab9f9c17fa636e60249b8d579521b2&"}, {"id": "1453292222714876045", "filename": "IMG_4626.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 770708, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1453292220974239857/1453292222714876045/IMG_4626.png?ex=69ff8e9a&is=69fe3d1a&hm=eac318d0a6121635eb26a21c570f2a7d3a06c99ccecb3f4d05e392aca150e519&"}, {"id": "1453292223188697169", "filename": "IMG_4629.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 757347, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1453292220974239857/1453292223188697169/IMG_4629.png?ex=69ff8e9a&is=69fe3d1a&hm=2cab920a4b7754ad4cb1ea2860a307dd56a1e3a09c2a2ef0769141f9bbc90eea&"}, {"id": "1453292223608131584", "filename": "IMG_4624.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 750146, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1453292220974239857/1453292223608131584/IMG_4624.png?ex=69ff8e9a&is=69fe3d1a&hm=a805156793d4d6f28118199cb9044fa224bf5c418ad6f051c4bc30849695409e&"}, {"id": "1453292224359174299", "filename": "IMG_4631.png"